es_selling_link',''),(3563,338,'_selling_services_list_6_services_selling_link','field_55b21af6aeab8'),(3564,338,'selling_services_list','7'),(3565,338,'_selling_services_list','field_55b21a5faeab6'),(3566,338,'services_buying_title','Services If You Are Buying'),(3567,338,'_services_buying_title','field_55b2398e8d6b6'),(3568,338,'services_buying_block_1_image','161'),(3569,338,'_services_buying_block_1_image','field_55b2399d8d6b7'),(3570,338,'services_buying_block_1_icon','163'),(3571,338,'_services_buying_block_1_icon','field_55b23aba8d6b8'),(3572,338,'services_buying_block_1_description','Whether you are buying or selling, Brigid’s speciality is taking coveted real estate in Westmount and Montreal, and matching its unique characteristics and features to the right individuals who will appreciate and cherish its charm and singularity.\r\nIf you are buying a home, Brigid can:\r\n\r\nHelp you find the ideal neighbourhood and living situation to fulfill your exact requests, including: price, amenities, location, space, style and condition.\r\nIf you do not have a mortgage broker she will direct you to the most reputable names in the business, ensuring that you clearly define your budget and means when buying the ideal living space.'),(3573,338,'_services_buying_block_1_description','field_55b23ad68d6b9'),(3574,338,'block_1_link',''),(3575,338,'_block_1_link','field_55b23d5fc60ab'),(3576,338,'services_buying_block_2_image','164'),(3577,338,'_services_buying_block_2_image','field_55b23af68d6ba'),(3578,338,'services_buying_block_2_icon','165'),(3579,338,'_services_buying_block_2_icon','field_55b23b0b8d6bb'),(3580,338,'services_buying_block_2_description','Help determine the area that interests you as your search criteria based on price and overall needs.'),(3581,338,'_services_buying_block_2_description','field_55b23b1b8d6bc'),(3582,338,'block_2_link',''),(3583,338,'_block_2_link','field_55b23d7cc60ac'),(3584,338,'additional_services_title','What Brigid Brings to the Table'),(3585,338,'_additional_services_title','field_55b23fe0dfc9b'),(3586,338,'additional_service_image','176'),(3587,338,'_additional_service_image','field_55b23feadfc9c'),(3588,338,'additional_service_description','Many times a home may need an expert to be able to stage it for best results and Brigid is able to assist in making your home present at its best\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Some tips from Brigid in preparing your home ready to be sold:</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>1)</strong> Eliminate all clutter, unnecessary household or decorative items, and furniture that may distract or discourage potential buyers.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>2)</strong> Make sure that kitchen and bathrooms are clean and tidy; visitors pay most attention to these rooms.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>3)</strong> If your house is bright, it will be more welcoming. Use mood lighting where possible, to make rooms cozy and warm.  Turn on all main lights and/or open curtains and blinds.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>4)</strong> Make sure faucets are not dripping and that all doors and casements close properly.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>5)</strong> Mow your lawn and make sure the rest of your yard is as well groomed as possible.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>6)</strong> Clear your entrance of puddles, snow, ice or leaves.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Understanding the Westmount Market</strong>\r\n\r\nMontreal’s real estate market is among the most complex and lucrative in Canada, particularly in Westmount. Renowned for being one of the best cities to live in nation-wide, this area has a rich history and vibrant community that is amplified by its unbeatable setting and surroundings. The homes here have been on Canada’s list of most prestigious real estate opportunities for decades, and brokering them requires an expert knowledge of their value, both monetarily and historically.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nMany homes here have distinctive attributes that can’t be found anywhere else in Canada, and it’s up to the broker to make sure these unique qualities are brought to the attention of the right buyer at the right time. Considerations like space, convenience, character, age and style all play a significant part in selling and purchasing a home in this area. Brigid’s expertise in this area is unparalleled, which is why she has sold every single one of her properties to the right buyers.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Understanding Her Clientele</strong>\r\n\r\nBrigid’s success in real estate in Westmount is due to her passion for her clients. Simply put, she strives to find the ideal homes for people who appreciate all that the area has to offer. One of her key traits is taking the time to get to know her clients, whether buyers and sellers, so she can ensure the best outcome possible for them. She focuses on details like budget, future plans, hobbies, lifestyle, daily routine, work, family life and personality for buyers, and factors like financial expectations, real estate goals and timeframes for sellers.\r\n\r\nMore importantly, she endeavors to keep communication open, honest and sincere throughout the entire process. This means that there are never any unexpected surprises, and every question, concern or query gets answered as quickly as possible. Her passion for providing authentic and dedicated services has made her name synonymous with real estate quality not just in Westmount, but also across Montreal.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Understanding the Area</strong>\r\n\r\nBrigid’s experience with Westmount and surrounding boroughs is undeniable. A Montrealer herself, she understands what sets this city apart from its surrounding boroughs, and what makes it valuable to buyers and sellers. From the beautiful British-influenced character homes to the modern, upscale townhomes, every street in the area has unique real estate to offer for those seeking the best in upscale Montreal living.\r\n\r\nShe also knows every detail about the landscape, from the best areas for stunning views and privacy, to the best areas for shopping and transportation convenience. All these details make the difference to a potential buyer, and her knowledge of them is one of the best in the industry.\r\n\r\nBook a consultation with her to see why she is respected and renowned for real estate in the area. Or, alternatively, look at her portfolio of homes sold and see why she has a stellar track record for matching the right home to the right buyer every time.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),(3589,338,'_additional_service_description','field_55b2401adfc9d'),(3590,338,'additional_service_link',''),(3591,338,'_additional_service_link','field_55b24165f47b5'),(3592,339,'inner_page_banner','102'),(3593,339,'_inner_page_banner','field_55b21604e7f4c'),(3594,339,'inner_page_description','Call Brigid today and she will help you through the buying and selling process.'),(3595,339,'_inner_page_description','field_55b2179956b78'),(3596,339,'services_selling_title','Services If You Are Selling'),(3597,339,'_services_selling_title','field_55b21a41aeab5'),(3598,339,'selling_services_list_0_services_selling_title','Property evaluation'),(3599,339,'_selling_services_list_0_services_selling_title','field_55b21ae0aeab7'),(3600,339,'selling_services_list_0_services_selling_link',''),(3601,339,'_selling_services_list_0_services_selling_link','field_55b21af6aeab8'),(3602,339,'selling_services_list_1_services_selling_title','Professional photography'),(3603,339,'_selling_services_list_1_services_selling_title','field_55b21ae0aeab7'),(3604,339,'selling_services_list_1_services_selling_link',''),(3605,339,'_selling_services_list_1_services_selling_link','field_55b21af6aeab8'),(3606,339,'selling_services_list_2_services_selling_title','Brokers’ caravan'),(3607,339,'_selling_services_list_2_services_selling_title','field_55b21ae0aeab7'),(3608,339,'selling_services_list_2_services_selling_link',''),(3609,339,'_selling_services_list_2_services_se