pen','open','','field_55b1eedfa7d31','','','2017-01-25 17:59:12','2017-01-25 17:59:12','',6,'http://brigidscullion.com/?post_type=acf-field&#038;p=24',13,'acf-field','',0),(25,1,'2015-07-24 07:56:13','2015-07-24 07:56:13','','footer-logo','','inherit','open','open','','footer-logo','','','2015-07-24 07:56:13','2015-07-24 07:56:13','',0,'http://brigidscullion.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/footer-logo.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(26,1,'2015-07-24 09:11:12','2015-07-24 09:11:12','<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"http://brigidscullion.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/nice-pic...but-crooked-teeth.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-362 size-medium alignleft\" src=\"http://brigidscullion.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/nice-pic...but-crooked-teeth-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Brigid is a Real Estate Broker with Groupe Sutton Centre-Ouest in Westmount, Montreal. All who have worked with her know that she offers her clients the very best representation throughout the many stages of buying or selling their home. She creates personalized and individualized marketing strategies for each of her clients. Brigid’s personable and professional character has allowed her to build and maintain solid client relationships.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Since becoming a broker, Brigid has sold every property she has listed and had a consistent record of finding homes to the complete satisfaction of her buyers. She has a determination that is unstoppable and is dedicated to “making it happen” for her clients.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">She describes her style as a “boutique” approach to buying and selling real estate. With a varied clientele, she understands that each person will have needs that are specific and unique…she makes it a priority to understand what those individual needs may be.</p>\r\n\r\n<h1>Montreal Real Estate in Westmount</h1>\r\nA beautiful community featuring Montreal’s most impressive real estate, Westmount has the most coveted homes in the city. Nestled on the western slope of Mount Royal, residences here are a combination of stately charm and modern allure.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThose seeking the ideal setting for family life, with large green spaces, shady trees and outstanding views of the city, will find it among Westmount’s lush and spacious streets. Residents here enjoy the perfect blend of calm quiet home life and urban conveniences like fashionable boutiques, eclectic art galleries and antique stores, in addition to world-renowned dining, gourmet markets and grocers.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Choosing the Right Home for You</h2>\r\nReal estate listings in Montreal are abundant, but finding the right homes for clients requires dedication to discovering and rediscovering the city and its distinct communities day after day. Brigid spends countless hours scouring the best features in Westmount, constantly seeking homes that have that vibrancy that sets them apart from the rest.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nTaking into consideration everything from the home’s surroundings and neighbourhood to the age and quality of its materials, she makes sure every clients wants and wishes for their new home is her priority. Finding your dream home situated along beautiful tree-lined streets or in the hub of the city and featuring their own independent spirit, Brigid can find it. Click <a href=\"http://brigidscullion.com/properties/\">here</a> to see the properties Brigid has listed and sold.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','About Brigid','','publish','open','open','','montreal-real-estate-agent','','','2017-01-24 20:25:56','2017-01-24 20:25:56','',0,'http://brigidscullion.com/?page_id=26',0,'page','',0),(28,1,'2015-07-24 09:11:26','2015-07-24 09:11:26','<h1>Real Estate in Westmount</h1>\r\nA distinct part of Montreal, Westmount is filled with culture, history, beauty and prime real estate. Nestled on the south face of the southern peak of the city’s famed mountain, Mont Royal, it features a beautiful array of sloping terrain filled with nature, calm and gorgeous views that extend from the summit to the end of the plateau at the foot of the mountain.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nAmidst all this greenery and tranquility, are some of Montreal’s most prized homes and real estate. From large grey stone mansions to stunning, brick town houses, around every turn amazing residences exist —many of which are waiting for the perfect buyers.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWhether you are buying or selling, Brigid’s speciality is taking coveted real estate in Westmount and Montreal, and matching its unique characteristics and features to the right individuals who will appreciate and cherish its charm and singularity.\r\n<h2>Tips for Selling</h2>\r\nMany times a home may need an expert to be able to stage it for best results and Brigid is able to assist in making your home present at its best.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSome tips from Brigid in preparing your home ready to be sold:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Eliminate all clutter, unnecessary household or decorative items, and furniture that may distract or discourage potential buyers.</li>\r\n 	<li>Make sure that kitchen and bathrooms are clean and tidy; visitors pay most attention to these rooms.</li>\r\n 	<li>If your house is bright, it will be more welcoming. Use mood lighting where possible, to make rooms cozy and warm.  Turn on all main lights and/or open curtains and blinds.</li>\r\n 	<li>Make sure faucets are not dripping and that all doors and casements close properly.</li>\r\n 	<li>Mow your lawn and make sure the rest of your yard is as well groomed as possible.</li>\r\n 	<li>Clear your entrance of puddles, snow, ice or leaves.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2>Understanding the Westmount Market</h2>\r\nMontreal’s real estate market is among the most complex and lucrative in Canada, particularly in Westmount. Renowned for being one of the best cities to live in nation-wide, this area has a rich history and vibrant community that is amplified by its unbeatable setting and surroundings. The homes here have been on Canada’s list of most prestigious real estate opportunities for decades, and brokering them requires an expert knowledge of their value, both monetarily and historically.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nMany homes here have distinctive attributes that can’t be found anywhere else in Canada, and it’s up to the agent to make sure these unique qualities are brought to the attention of the right buyer at the right time. Considerations like space, convenience, character, age and style all play a significant part in selling and purchasing a home in this area. Brigid’s expertise in this area is unparalleled, which is why she has sold every single one of her properties to the right buyers.\r\n<h2>Understanding Her Clientele</h2>\r\nBrigid’s success in real estate in Westmount is due to her passion for her clients. Simply put, she strives to find the ideal homes for people who appreciate all that the area has to offer. One of her key traits is taking the time to get to know her clients, whether buyers and sellers, so she can ensure the best outcome possible for them. She focuses on details like budget, future plans, hobbies, lifestyle, daily routine, work, family life and personality for buyers, and factors like financial expectations, real estate goals and timeframes for sellers.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nMore importantly, she endeavours to keep communication open, honest and sincere throughout the entire process. This means that there are never any unexpected surprises, and every question, concern or query gets answered as quickly as possible. Her passion for providing authentic and dedicated services has made her name synonymous with real estate quality not just in Westmount, but also across Montreal.\r\n<h2>Understanding the Area</h2>\r\nBrigid’s experience with the Westmount area is undeniable. A Montrealer herself, she understands what sets this city apart from its surrounding boroughs, and what makes it valuable to buyers and sellers. From the beautiful British-influenced character homes to the modern, upscale townhomes, every street in the area has unique real estate to offer for those seeking the best in upscale Montreal living.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nShe also knows every detail about the landscape, from the best areas for stunning views and privacy, to the best areas for shopping and transportation convenience. All these details make the difference to a potential buyer, and her knowledge of them is the best in the industry.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBook a consultation with her to see why she is respected and renowned for real estate in the area. Or, alternatively, look at her portfolio of homes for sale and see why she has a stellar track record for matching the right home to the right buyer every time.','Services','','publish','open','open','','montreal-luxury-real-estate-services','','','2017-02-10 20:15:59','2017-02-10 20:15:59','',0,'http://brigidscullion.com/?page_id=28',0,'page','',0),(30,1,'2015-07-24 09:11:46','2015-07-24 09:11:46','No matter what style of home you are looking to buy, Brigid knows what can be perfect for you. With a knack for finding the best gems in the community that offers an extensive range of style and sizes for every lifestyle.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSee what Brigid’s clients have said about her and browse her previous successful transactions. Every property features unique characteristics, from history and craftsmanship to style and functionality. Likewise, the range of locations are suited to every kind of lifestyle, whether it’s active family life and outdoor enthusiasm, or quiet, suburban privacy nestled away from the bustle.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<h2>Types of Properties</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Historic Grey Stone Mansions</strong>\r\n\r\nWestmount is famed for opulent grey stone mansions that overlook the beautiful scenery of Montreal. These homes are built with some of the best craftsmanship in the country, and have historic backgrounds that add value and character to every inch of their makeup. Featuring authentic stained glass, wrought iron details and immaculately designed interiors and gardens, these homes have some of the highest real estate value in Canada.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Classic Victorian Homes</strong>\r\n\r\nOften referred to as Queen Anne properties, these coveted Westmount homes for sale feature Tudor timbres, intricate woodwork, large columns and arched windows. Heavily inspired by classic British architecture, they serve as iconic and historic emblems of some of Montreal\'s best residential architecture.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Modern Townhouses and Homes</strong>\r\n\r\nWestmount is also home to some of the city\'s most stunning modern designs too. Often featuring beautiful red brick exteriors and charming stoop steps, these townhomes and homes are built with sleek and tasteful contemporary designs and only the best materials available. From beautiful hardwood floors and large windows to open-concept kitchens, lofts and floating stairs, these living spaces are the epitome of modern style.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nContact Brigid to find the perfect living space for you. Always in tune with all homes for sale in Westmount, she will guide you to the ideal property suited to your budget, lifestyle and individual needs. A private consultation will uncover all the important aspects you need to look for when buying a home here, including future plans, daily routine and important details about the distinctive neighbourhoods. With her extensive knowledge, you’ll find the perfect property in no time.','Properties','','publish','open','open','','properties','','','2015-10-22 00:23:11','2015-10-22 00:23:11','',0,'http://brigidscullion.com/?page_id=30',0,'page','',0),(32,1,'2015-07-24 09:11:58','2015-07-24 09:11:58','','Testimonials','','publish','open','open','','testimonials','','','2015-08-04 13:42:43','2015-08-04 13:42:43'