 her full attention and made a 100% effort to understand the Buyers needs as well as my own.\r\n\r\nBrigid displayed great patience and creative problem solving to arrive at a mutually satisfying agreement\".','testimonial 2','','publish','closed','closed','','testimonial-2','','','2015-07-30 14:09:13','2015-07-30 14:09:13','',0,'http://brigidscullion.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=197',0,'testimonial','',0),(198,1,'2015-07-27 11:35:54','2015-07-27 11:35:54','\"It was a pleasure looking for our first home with Brigid, even though this purchase proved to be a more daunting task than we initially thought. Her patience throughout the process helped keep our focus on our end-goal and she respected our need to take all the time necessary to make a thoughtful decision. Her ability to understand our needs and preferences led us to our ultimate choice.\r\n\r\nAbove and beyond her professionalism and friendliness, she provided us with market insight and data that helped us understand the rationale behind property valuations. This ensured that we were comfortable with every one of our decisions throughout the process. This would not have been possible had we opted to not work with a broker. Thankfully, working with Brigid led us to a beautiful home that we will be able to enjoy for years to come\".','testimonial 3','','publish','closed','closed','','testimonial-3','','','2015-07-31 09:03:37','2015-07-31 09:03:37','',0,'http://brigidscullion.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=198',0,'testimonial','',0),(199,1,'2015-07-27 11:36:29','2015-07-27 11:36:29','\"Vito et moi venons vous remercier chaleureusement pour le travail impeccable que vous avez fait autour de la vente de sa maison. Me Blier nous a avisés hier que les fonds étaient rendus dans le compte de Vito. C\'est un immense soulagement! Malgré les difficultés et les délais dûs à la situation particulière, tout s\'est finalement bien passé. Vous avez été très généreuse de votre temps et nous vous en sommes reconnaissants