y customized (millwork) wood built-ins.</li>\r\n 	<li>Habitat 67 Tennis Club in clay courts with instructor.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nHabitat\'67 is a Limited Partnership and the General Partner will look after the transfer of title with a cost of 1 % of the sale price, payable by the Buyer to the Partnership. However, there is no welcome tax. Also, there are no notary costs pertaining to the transfer of title, except in the event of financing.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nHabitat\'67 was cited as a heritage building by the city of Montreal in September 2007, and declared a heritage building by the Government of Quebec in February 2009 in relation to the outside of the Complex as well as to the inside of the 4 cubes that belong to the architect, renowned internationally, Mr. Moshe Safdie.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 2\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<h3>Inclusions</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 2\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n\r\nTHE FOLLOWING APPLIANCES: WHIRLPOOL WASHER &amp; DRYER, DACOR DISHWASHER, FAGOR-INDUCTION COOKTOP, FISHER &amp; PAYKEL FRIDGEDAIRE, PANASONIC MICROWAVE, KITCHENAID OVEN, BROAN RANGE HOOD. LIGHTING FIXTURE IN DINING ROOM, LIGHTING FIXTURE OVER KITCHEN ISLAND, SPLIT AIR CONDITIONER UNIT.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"column\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','2600 Pierre-Dupuy','','publish','closed','closed','','2600-pierre-dupuy','','','2017-02-10 05:11:24','2017-02-10 05:11:24','',0,'http://brigidscullion.com/?post_type=property&#038;p=1041',14,'property','',0),(1064,4,'2017-02-09 02:57:36','2017-02-09 02:57:36','<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 2\">\