etely re-done in 2012 with heated floors. The bathroom was completed with a separate shower and soaker tub, playroom, laundry room with a large walk-in closet and mud room with separate entrance.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 3\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n\r\nAlso included is an integrated 2 car garage and garden.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n\r\nThis home has so much original detailing that it is definitely worth the visit! It would be my pleasure to show you how lovely it is.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','3742 The Boulevard','','publish','closed','closed','','3742-the-boulevard','','','2017-02-10 03:45:45','2017-02-10 03:45:45','',0,'http://brigidscullion.com/?post_type=property&#038;p=1083',5,'property','',0),(1122,4,'2017-02-09 03:06:19','2017-02-09 03:06:19',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','1122','','','2017-02-10 06:18:25','2017-02-10 06:18:25','',0,'http://brigidscullion.com/?p=1122',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1123,4,'2017-02-09 03:14:21','2017-02-09 03:14:21','<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 2\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n\r\nElegant &amp; classic Westmount home-Lovingly maintained &amp; enjoyed for over 40 years. The property faces south west &amp; has beautiful natural light &amp; stunning views. 4 bedrooms, 2 fireplaces, 3 balconies, 1 car integrated garage and 5 exterior parking. Exceptional home that is worth the visit!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 2\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<h3>FEATURES</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Unobstructed views facing south.</li>\r\n 	<li>Basement has its own back entrance.</li>\r\n 	<li>Gorgeous leaded glass windows.</li>\r\n 	<li>Skylights.</li>\r\n 	<li>High ceilings.</li>